                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-437-18750816 t18750816-437-punishment-22"></join>Eighteen Months' Imprisonment.</rs>
                  </hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="largeCaps">EMILINE JOHN</hi>—<hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <rs id="t18750816-437-verdict-2" type="verdictDescription">
